    <item>
      <title>联合国难民署报告称，2023 年全球将有近 1.2 亿人流离失所</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/11/nx-s1-5002273/nearly-120-million-people-were-displaced-around-the-world-in-2023-unhcr-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国难民事务办公室发现，截至去年年底，每 69 人中就有 1 人被迫离开家园——无论是在本国境内还是跨越国际边界。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/06/11/nx-s1-5002273/nearly-120-million-people-were-displaced-around-the-world-in-2023-unhcr-report-says</guid>
